"info_text" : "これはネイティブの Android Ethereum 軽量クライアントウォレットです。

go-ethereum プロジェクトから、Ethereum 軽量クライアントとしてインプロセスノードを使用します。

karalabe, fjl, zsfelfoldi および obscuren の素晴らしい仕事に大変感謝します!

このアルファは rinkeby testnet を使用します。

CRYPTOSTARS は可能な限り分散化しようとしています。 したがって、集中型の事前構成済みのノードではなく、軽いクライアントを使用しています。 残念ながら、まだ完全に分散化することはできません。 (フィアット) 参照の為替レートを取得するために、cryptocompare に照会し、素晴らしい etherscan.io サービスを使用してトランダクションを取得します。 何かの理由でこれらのサービスがダウンしてもアプリは動作しますが、為替レートの更新などの一部の機能は使えません。 これらのものが分散化されて入手できるようになると、すぐにそれを使用しようとします。

素晴らしいアイコンは Michael Cook の作成です。

これはアルファ版であり、バグがあるかもしれないことにご注意ください。 これ または これ ような既知のバグがあるかもしれません。

プロジェクトは ligi によって、ウォレットとしてのみの必要性からだけでなく espass プロジェクトのビルディングブロックとして始まりました

プロジェクトは無料のソフトウェアです (別名 FOSS/フリー/オープンソース) - CRYPTOSTARS GitHub 組織 でコードを見たり、問題を報告することができます

このアプリですばらしい時間をお過ごしください。フィードバック、寄付、プルリクエストをお待ちしています ..-)

フィードバックの理想的な場所は、sub-reddit https://www.reddit.com/r/walleth です ソースは github で見つけることができます"

"info_text" : "This is a native Android Ethereum light client wallet.

It uses the in process node as ethereum light client from the go-ethereum project.

Big shout out to karalabe, fjl, zsfelfoldi and obscuren here - awesome work!

This alpha uses the rinkeby testnet.

CRYPTOSTARS is trying to be as decentralized as possible. Hence it is using a light client and not centralized pre-configured nodes. Unfortunately we cannot be fully decentralized yet. For getting the exchange rates for (fiat) references we are querying cryptocompare and to get transactions we use the great etherscan.io service. The app will work if these services are down for some reason - but you might miss some features like up to date exchange rates. As soon as it is possible to get these things in a decentralized manner we will try to use it.

Our wonderful Icon is from Michael Cook.

Be aware that this is an alpha and there will be bugs. There are also some known issues like this one and this one

The project was started by ligi as this is not only needed as a wallet - but also as a building block for the espass project

The project is libre software (aka FOSS/free/open source) - you can find code and open issues on the CRYPTOSTARS GitHub Organisation

Please have a great time with this app and we are happy about feedback, donations, pull-requests ..-)

The ideal place for feedback is our sub-reddit https://www.reddit.com/r/walleth You can find the source on github"

"info_text" : "All CRYPTOSTARS coins are built on the blockchain technology. A blockchain functions as a secure, public ledger of all transactions on a peer-to-peer network that cannot be tampered with except through the use of an impractically large amount of computing power. A complete copy of the ledger is stored on each node in the network, allowing for such security. Specifically, CRYPTOSTARS is built on the Ethereum blockchain in order to achieve a completely decentralized system. The benefits of a decentralized system are numerous. Firstly, on a decentralized system, there is less likely to be a single point of failure on the network. In a centralized system, if the central node in the network fails, the whole network fails with it. However, in a decentralized system, the network’s data and computational power is distributed among many nodes, requiring a larger number of nodes to fail before the network is seriously impacted by the failures. Secondly, by distributing computing resources across a decentralized system, as the network grows, so too does the computational power of the network. Finally, in conjunction with blockchain technology, a decentralized network allows transactions to be independently verified by any node in the network, eliminating the need for trust in a central institution to verify transactions for everyone. As the benefits of a decentralized network become more apparent, it is clear that the future of the web (sometimes called Web 3.0) is a decentralized one."

playstore_details.title: Crypto Blockchain Wallet to Buy & Sell Bitcoin
playstore_details.description:
Cryptostars is The leading multi-platform  Bitcoin Cash wallet to buy and sell Cryptocurrency.
CRYPTOSTARS is built on blockchain technology.
 A blockchain functions as a secure, public ledger of all transactions on a peer-to-peer network that cannot be tampered with except through the use of an impractically large amount of computing power.
A complete copy of the ledger is stored on each node in the network, allowing for such security.
Specifically, CRYPTO-STARS is built on the Ethereum blockchain in order to achieve a completely decentralised system.

BEST FEATURES:

• No registration, web service or cloud required! This wallet is  peer to peer.
• Less is more: No support for alt-coins or tokens. No unnecessary features.
• Buy Bitcoin with ease
• Protect your information with advanced Two-Factor Authentication
• Find out where you can spend Bitcoin
• Bitcoin (BTC) & Bitcoin Cash (BCH) support
• Conversion to and from national currencies.
• Sending and receiving of Bitcoin via NFC, QR-codes or Bitcoin URLs.
• Send Bitcoin, Ethereum, Bitcoin Cash  instantly to anyone in the world
• When you're offline, you can still pay bitcoins via Bluetooth.
• System notification for sent coins and received coins.
• Sweeping of paper wallets 
• App widget for ease request of Bitcoin balance.
• Request payments in cryptocurrencies with ease
